---
---
<div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr]">
  <div class="rounded-[2rem] bg-navy p-7 text-white shadow-soft">
    <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-violet-200">Contact the institute</p>
    <h3 class="mt-4 font-display text-3xl font-black">Need help with admission?</h3>
    <p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-200">Parents and students can use the enquiry form or contact placeholders below. Replace placeholder contact details before launch.</p>
    <div class="mt-8 space-y-5 text-sm leading-6">
      <p><strong class="block text-white">Institute</strong>Alkesh Dinesh Mody Institute for Financial & Management Studies</p>
      <p><strong class="block text-white">Address</strong>Joraver Bhavan, University of Mumbai, Vidyanagari Campus, Santacruz (E), Mumbai - 400098</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-1 xl:grid-cols-3">
      <a class="rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-3 text-center text-sm font-extrabold text-navy" href="#">Call: To be updated</a>
      <a class="rounded-full bg-emerald-500 px-4 py-3 text-center text-sm font-extrabold text-white" href="#">WhatsApp: To be updated</a>
      <a class="rounded-full bg-violet-500 px-4 py-3 text-center text-sm font-extrabold text-white" href="mailto:email-to-be-updated@example.com">Email placeholder</a>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 flex min-h-56 items-center justify-center rounded-3xl border border-dashed border-violet-300 bg-white/10 p-6 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-violet-100">
      Google Maps embed placeholder<br />Replace with official map iframe before launch.
    </div>
  </div>
  <form class="rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-card sm:p-8" action="#" method="post" aria-label="Admission enquiry form">
    <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-black text-navy">Admission enquiry form</h3>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">Static form prepared for later Google Forms or Formspree integration. No backend is connected yet.</p>
    <div class="mt-6 grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <label class="text-sm font-bold text-navy">Student Name<input class="mt-2 w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 px-4 py-3 font-normal outline-none focus:border-purple focus:ring-4 focus:ring-violet-100" name="student_name" autocomplete="name" placeholder="Enter student name" /></label>
      <label class="text-sm font-bold text-navy">Mobile Number<input class="mt-2 w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 px-4 py-3 font-normal outline-none focus:border-purple focus:ring-4 focus:ring-violet-100" name="mobile" inputmode="tel" autocomplete="tel" placeholder="Enter mobile number" /></label>
      <label class="text-sm font-bold text-navy">Email<input class="mt-2 w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 px-4 py-3 font-normal outline-none focus:border-purple focus:ring-4 focus:ring-violet-100" name="email" type="email" autocomplete="email" placeholder="Enter email address" /></label>
      <label class="text-sm font-bold text-navy">Class 12 Stream<input class="mt-2 w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 px-4 py-3 font-normal outline-none focus:border-purple focus:ring-4 focus:ring-violet-100" name="class_12_stream" placeholder="Commerce / Science / Arts" /></label>
      <label class="text-sm font-bold text-navy sm:col-span-2">Message<textarea class="mt-2 min-h-32 w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 px-4 py-3 font-normal outline-none focus:border-purple focus:ring-4 focus:ring-violet-100" name="message" placeholder="Ask your admission question"></textarea></label>
    </div>
    <button class="btn-primary mt-6 w-full sm:w-auto" type="submit">Submit Enquiry</button>
  </form>
</div>
